OL,3,CMan who took axe into mosque 'had zip
OL,4,Cties and balaclava'
OL,6,FA man accused of entering a mosque
OL,7,Fwith an axe, a hammer and a knife also
OL,8,Fallegedly took in zip ties and a
OL,9,Fbalaclava, a court has heard.
OL,11,FDarren Connor, 55, appeared on 27
OL,12,FFebruary at Manchester Magistrates'
OL,13,FCourt where he denied possession of an
OL,14,Foffensive weapon in a public place
OL,15,Fwithout lawful authority or reasonable
OL,16,Fexcuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
