FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772287406
OL,3,CMan who took axe into mosque 'had zip
OL,4,Cties and balaclava'
OL,6,FProsecutor Gareth Hughes said the
OL,7,Fdefendant, a white Briton, is said to
OL,8,Fhave attended Manchester Central
OL,9,FMosque during Ramadan prayers on the
OL,10,Fevening of 24 February.
OL,12,FMr Hughes told the court a
OL,13,F"considerable number of people" were
OL,14,Fin the Victoria Park mosque at the
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,FConnor was found to be in possession
OL,18,Fof an axe, a hammer and a Stanley
OL,19,Fknife, said the prosecutor, and "in
OL,20,Faddition" had zip ties and a balaclava.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@_O]{D@aOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772287406
OL,3,CMan who took axe into mosque 'had zip
OL,4,Cties and balaclava'
OL,6,FThe defendant, wearing a yellow high-
OL,7,Fvisibility jacket and a black and grey
OL,8,Fchecked shirt, entered a not guilty
OL,9,Fplea to the allegation.
OL,11,FDistrict Judge Lucy Hogarth told
OL,12,FConnor that the nature and
OL,13,Fcircumstances of the charge meant the
OL,14,Fcase needed to be allocated to the
OL,15,FCrown Court.
OL,17,FConnor, of Gorton Road, Stockport,
OL,18,Falso faced an allegation of possession
OL,19,Fof cannabis, also on 24 February,
OL,20,Fwhich he admitted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772287406
OL,3,CMan who took axe into mosque 'had zip
OL,4,Cties and balaclava'
OL,6,FHe was remanded in custody to next
OL,7,Fappear at Manchester Crown Court on 3
OL,8,FApril where both matters will be dealt
OL,9,Fwith.
OL,11,FNo application for bail was made by
OL,12,Fhis solicitor.
OL,14,FEarlier, police said a second man who
OL,15,Fwas arrested in connection with the
OL,16,Fincident will face no further action.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
