PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772287406
OL,3,CMan who took axe into mosque 'had zip
OL,4,Cties and balaclava'
OL,6,FChairman of the mosque Hamad Khan
OL,7,Fpreviously said a man entered the
OL,8,Fmosque at about 8.30pm on 24 February
OL,9,Fwhen around 1,500 people were saying
OL,10,FRamadan prayers.
OL,12,FMr Khan said the suspect was ushered
OL,13,Finto an office and police were called
OL,14,Fafter an axe was spotted in his bag.
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
